data.description: Come check out this fully occupied turnkey duplex in the popular West Boulevard neighborhood on Cleveland's west side.  This property was recently renovated in the past few years and is currently getting $1,485 in rent.  You'll love the renovated bathrooms and kitchen with new flooring throughout.  The roof was replaced in 2022, as well as a lot of the decking and lots of exterior repairs.  This property is ready to go and looking for a new owner who would like to start making income Day 1!
